orts</a></li><li class="ftr-blk__column-list-item"><a class="ftr-blk__column-list-item-lnk trackXiti" href="/insolite/"  title="" data-xiti-libelle="insolite" data-xiti="footer" data-xiti-type="N">Insolite</a></li><li class="ftr-blk__column-list-item"><a class="ftr-blk__column-list-item-lnk trackXiti" href="https://www.lci.fr/elections/resultats/" target="_blank"  title="" data-xiti-libelle="resultats-elections-municipales-2020" data-xiti="footer" data-xiti-type="N">Résultats Élections Municipales 2020</a></li></ul><p class="ftr-blk__column-title trackXiti" data-xiti-libelle="societe" data-xiti="footer" data-xiti-type="N"><a href="/actu-societe/">SOCIÉTÉ</a></p><ul class="ftr-blk__column-list"><li class="ftr-blk__column-list-item"><a class="ftr-blk__column-list-item-lnk trackXiti" href="/social/"  title="" data-xiti-libelle="social" data-xiti="footer" data-xiti-type="N">Social</a></li><li class="ftr-blk__column-list-item"><a class="ftr-blk__column-list-item-lnk trackXiti" href="/population/"  title="" data-xiti-libelle="population" data-xiti="footer" data-xiti-type="N">Population</a></li><li class="ftr-blk__column-list-item"><a class="ftr-blk__column-list-item-lnk trackXiti" href="/education/"  title="" data-xiti-libelle="education" data-xiti="footer" data-xiti-type="N">Education</a></li><li class="ftr-blk__column-list-item"><a class="ftr-blk__column-list-item-lnk trackXiti" href="/sante/"  title="" data-xiti-libelle="sante" data-xiti="footer" data-xiti-type="N">Santé</a></li></ul><p class="ftr-blk__column-title trackXiti" data-xiti-libelle="daily" data-xiti="footer" data-xiti-type="N"><a href="/daily/">DAILY</a></p><ul class="ftr-blk__column-list"><li class="ftr-blk__column-list-item"><a class="ftr-blk__column-list-item-lnk trackXiti" href="/famille/"  title="" data-xiti-libelle="famille" data-xiti="footer" data-xiti-type="N">Famille</a></li><li class="ftr-blk__column-list-item"><a class="ftr-blk__column-list-item-lnk trackXiti" href="/vie-de-couple/"  title="" dat